  <brief_title>A Study to Evaluate the Safety and Efficacy of PAC-14028 Cream in Rosacea</brief_title>
  <official_title>Multicenter, Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled Parallel-group, Dose Finding Phase II Clinical Trial to Evaluate Anti Rosacea Effect and Safety of PAC-14028 Cream (0.1%, 0.3%, 1.0%) in Rosacea Patients</official_title>
