  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This clinical study is to determine the optimum dose of PAC-14028 cream in a therapeutic
      confirmatory clinical study by evaluating the safety and therapeutic equivalence of PAC-14028
      cream 0.1%, 0.3% and 1.0% in patients with rosacea.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
